headline: 16 Northern Illinois Communities Take Steps to Become EV Ready with ComEd
summary: CHICAGO, October 28, 2025--ComEd and the Metropolitan Mayors Caucus (Caucus) today announced the fourth cohort of communities participating in the award-winning EV Readiness Program, a unique initiative to help local governments in Illinois prepare for the growing demand for electric vehicles (EVs) and EV charging infrastructure.
